  "body": "# Description\r\nAs an operator of a Besu node, I want to be able to use DNS discovery to complement UDP-based discovery, using the mechanism defined with EIP-1459. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* An operator can define a host to start DNS discovery from (ex: example.com).\r\n* In the absence of an explicit host, if the operator runs a named network (mainnet, ropsten), it uses the proper host name.\r\n* DNS discovery may be explicitly disabled.\r\n\r\n",
